These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, d&b, hip-hop, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, australian, french, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, golf, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the malaysian is the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
3. the mexican is in an odd position##4
4. the french is not the fan of pop##6
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the malaysian##6
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the mexican##3
7. the mexican is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the australian##7
8. the person who's sport is handball is between the fan of d&b and the fan of hip-hop##2
9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | ambient      | d&b   | pop  |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | french   | mexican | australian  |
| Sport         | snowboarding | handball | volleyball     | golf |

