.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, fanta, coffee
There 4 different types of food: potato, artichoke, strawberry, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, russian, spanish, italian
 1. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating artichoke##6
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person eating potato is the spanish##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is the italian##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the russian##3
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the person drinking fanta##7
10. the spanish is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | milk | mirinda         | fanta    | coffee  |
| Food          | avocado     | artichoke | potato | strawberry |
| Nationality   | indonesian     | russian     | spanish  | italian |

