.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, drawing, dancing, hiking
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, colombian, canadian
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, trike, helicopter
1. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
4. the mexican is between the canadian and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person driving the helicopter##6
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the malaysian##7
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | dancing  | drawing  | singing |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | colombian | mexican | canadian     |
| Transport     | helicopter    | motorbike     | snowmobile     | trike         |

