.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, classical, trance, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, french, polish, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, boat, trike
1. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
2. the french is the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the fan of classical is the person driving the car##1
5. the polish is the fan of indie##1
6. the russian is the person driving the scooter##1
7. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
8. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the fan of classical and the fan of trance##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | rock     | indie   | trance      |
| Nationality   | french    | russian | polish | egyptian  |
| Transport     | car | scooter  | trike    | boat |

