.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, techno, indie, jazz
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, hedgehog, chinchilla
1. the person drinking 7up is not the fan of jazz##6
2. the fan of techno is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the fan of metal##7
3. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person drinking mirinda##7
5. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the fan of metal is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | 7up | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | indie  | techno  | metal    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | guinea-pig  | ferret    | hedgehog    |

