.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, gardening, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, japanese, russian, turkish
1. the turkish is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
3. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking cola##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
8. the person drinking coffee is not the italian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | milk     | coffee | cola        | iced-tea       |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing    | reading | board-games |
| Nationality   | turkish     | japanese  | italian    | russian   |

