4. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
5. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
7. the nurse is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the bike##7
8. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
9. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
