The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, disaster, epic
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, guinea-pig, turtle
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 7. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching epic movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | singing | writing      | camping | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | documentary | animation  | epic       |
| Pet           | turtle         | guinea-pig       | rabbit    | hamster  |

