5. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
7. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
8. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
