There are 4 different nationalities: thai, malaysian, british, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, scooter, taxi, airplane
 1. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the taxi is between the malaysian and the british##2
 5. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 7. the malaysian is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 8. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking iced-tea##7
 9. the thai is somewhere to the left of the british##5
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
11. the thai is between the british and the malaysian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | lemonade     | hot-chocolate      | coffee     |
| Nationality   | dutch  | malaysian   | thai   | british |
| Transport     | airplane     | subway | taxi | scooter   |

