.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-14::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cabbage, lettuce, banana
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, climbing, cricket
1. the fan of country is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the fan of punk##7
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the fan of country##7
3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
5. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the fan of classical##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of country##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
8. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
9. the person who's sport is climbing is not the fan of classical##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | pumpkin | banana | lettuce          | cabbage  |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | classical      | country    | punk   |
| Sport         | volleyball | biathlon  | climbing | cricket |

