4. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
5. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person eating strawberry##5
6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating apple##1
7. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
8. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |      4       |
