 4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person watching adventure movies##6
 5. the accountant is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the frog##7
 6. the accountant is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the police-officer is the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | security-guard  | accountant | dressmaker | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | documentary     | animation      | comedy    |
